Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Political TV commercials
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf1p
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Oct 1984
How the young are getting their political understanding - from 30-second TV commercials. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less